:SKRSLUT.
.br
Payment of compensation is conditional upon all treatment and
transport being performed by arrangement with SOS International. As
such, it is SOS International which decides when and how
repatriation is to take place. Therefore, SOS International must
always be contacted before any kind of treatment or transport is
initiated.
